                type: 'text',
                title: '',
                info: 'Strengthen the foundation',
                data: '<p>The syllabus of XIth & XIIth is the main foundation of Biology & Chemistry that students are expected to learn. Therefore, you must prefer to read the academic science textbooks of these two years to cover all the basics of biology. Reading unnecessary study material is not a smart approach to absorb the crux of biology compared to learning these foundational books of secondary school.</p>'
