                type: 'text',
                title: '',
                info: ' Find the similarities in the topics',
                data: '<p>Another recommendation for the students while studying biology or even other subjects is to find the common lessons between two different subjects. It indirectly reserves ample of time & also helps you to bring clarity in your deeper understanding of the concept.</p><p><b>E.G.</b> Chapter 2: Structure of Atoms & Chapter 3: Atoms & Nuclear included in the chemistry subject has a similar pattern to some part of modern physics.</p>'
