                data: '<p>Due to large competition for securing seats in best medical colleges in India, many of the medical aspirants always ask a common question which is, how to prepare for NEET exam and clear it in the first attempt?</p><p>There should be a good strategy which students should follow in order to secure a seat in any of the top medical colleges in the country.</p><p>The syllabus for NEET exam is really vast but if students have a well-structured study plan they can easily clear it.</p>'
