                "info": "",
                "data": "<p><b><u>Step 1</u>: Registration</b></p> To take part in Punjab NEET Counselling 2022, it is mandatory for the candidate to sign up at the legitimate internet site of BFUHS. Candidates who fail to sign up in the stipulated time frame will now no longer be eligible for Punjab NEET 2022 Counselling.</p>"
