                data: '<P>Do you want to know about the Maharashtra NEET Counselling 2022 dates, or the Maharashtra NEET UG Counselling process and other important things related to it? Then, let’s get started!!</P><p><b>The Commissioner, State CET CELL, Mumbai,</b> has released an application for NEET 2022. It is an authority who conducts the admission process for the courses on health & science to the colleges in Maharashtra state. The eligible candidates may apply to any Public / Private, & reserved colleges within the State of Maharashtra.</p><p>For admission to the state quota seats in Government/ corporation, Government Aided and all the quota seats in private/ minority colleges of Maharashtra state, the Maharashtra NEET counselling 2021 for UG is conducted. Students or applicants have to first register themselves on the official website of CET cell and then they can fill the online application form.</p>'
