                "data": '<p>The phase of shifting abroad involves a great deal of preparation - packing clothes and other materials, legal papers, budget management. In such cases, a checklist is important for tracking down the things for which you don’t want to take any chances of missing out. </p><p>We have provided a comprehensive list of items that any student needs while living abroad for education. Check them below and add it in your list when you start packing up your stuff.</p>'
