                data: '<p>There are various aspects to all these 4 kinds of universities. In this blog, we will understand <a href="https://www.selectyouruniversity.com/blog/what-is-deemed-university.php" target="_blank">what a deemed university</a> is and a list of all deemed universities in India.</p>'
